text.section:
Upon approval of the economic improvement plan and annual budget, the board shall:
Submit the budget to the Department for Local Government as provided in KRS 65A.020;
Publish pursuant to KRS Chapter 424 and mail by first-class mail to each affected property owner a description of the plan, the fair basis of assessment to be utilized, the estimated cost to the property owner, and the ratio that the cost to each property owner bears to the total cost of the economic improvements.
